SCIM tokens management commands.

USAGE:
  scw iam scim-tokens <command>

AVAILABLE COMMANDS:
  create      Create a SCIM token
  delete      Delete a SCIM token
  list        List SCIM tokens

FLAGS:
  -h, --help                help for scim-tokens
      --list-sub-commands   List all subcommands

GLOBAL FLAGS:
  -c, --config string    The path to the config file
  -D, --debug            Enable debug mode
  -o, --output string    Output format: json or human, see 'scw help output' for more info (default "human")
  -p, --profile string   The config profile to use

Use "scw iam scim-tokens [command] --help" for more information about a command.
